{"tid":1945213,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"侵 簽左台灣法案","createTime":"2020-03-27T02:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T10:39:34.000Z","uid":88663,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1bbeef009014ba0199b32982289f4112b4e98c72","tid":1945213,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:07:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://share.881903.com/?news_id=1276739&amp;category_id=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshare.881903.com%2F%3Fnews_id%3D1276739%26category_id%3D0&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=633b60e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://share.881903.com/?news_id=1276739&amp;category_id=0</a>"},{"pid":"d6730c05e53d551d6a2e098460569aec268f007e","tid":1945213,"uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:08:35.000Z","msg":"特朗普正式簽署「台灣法案」<br />\n27.03.2020 09:54<br />\n美國總統特朗普正式簽署「台灣法案」，是繼「台灣旅行法」後，另一個以台灣命名的美國法律。「台灣法案」要求美國行政部門支持台灣強化正式外交關係，貿易代表署亦應與美國國會協商，尋求增進美台雙邊經貿關係。在國際參與方面，法案要求華府在適當情況下，支持台灣在所有並非以主權國家為參與資格的國際組織，成為會員，並在其他適當組織中，取得觀察員身份。法案又呼籲華府對於台灣造成傷害的國家，應該考慮改變與有關國家的經濟、安全及外交接觸。"},{"pid":"9e793202d5bdc9c8adff17aa68697a78307c876d","tid":1945213,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快到"},{"pid":"49538cff029622800caa2feca49fe66940553d46","tid":1945213,"uid":88663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:09:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://share.881903.com/?news_id=1276734&amp;category_id=367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshare.881903.com%2F%3Fnews_id%3D1276734%26category_id%3D367&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=12ebc310\" target=\"_blank\">https://share.881903.com/?news_id=1276734&amp;category_id=367</a><br />\n華府或限制製造商向華為供應晶片"},{"pid":"2a7ffb89b6343687bc1c86eb4d70acc94de8010d","tid":1945213,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6730c05e53d551d6a2e098460569aec268f007e","tid":1945213,"uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:08:35.000Z","msg":"特朗普正式簽署「台灣法案」<br />\n27.03.2020 09:54<br />\n美國總統特朗普正式簽署「台灣法案」，是繼「台灣旅行法」後，另一個以台灣命名的美國法律。「台灣法案」要求美國行政部門支持台灣強化正式外交關係，貿易代表署亦應與美國國會協商，尋求增進美台雙邊經貿關係。在國際參與方面，法案要求華府在適當情況下，支持台灣在所有並非以主權國家為參與資格的國際組織，成為會員，並在其他適當組織中，取得觀察員身份。法案又呼籲華府對於台灣造成傷害的國家，應該考慮改變與有關國家的經濟、安全及外交接觸。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:10:26.000Z","msg":"Thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46ae9d4ae41da3433992d34f429da0eb8a05f36","tid":1945213,"uid":186010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:10:44.000Z","msg":"戰機有用了"},{"pid":"b24fec4c258cfb834d0eac450214358e3343e77a","tid":1945213,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:21:03.000Z","msg":"台灣抗疫有功<br />\n梗係要拉攏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845b221623616884cf8c81209550ed554cf74bb1","tid":1945213,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:22:44.000Z","msg":"台灣獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9670ffec0d94dc4192b2126f6b8f7fc53d7309","tid":1945213,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:36:53.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"32a3a1c8862dbdcaddf551eb288a529ac2d9d236","tid":1945213,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49538cff029622800caa2feca49fe66940553d46","tid":1945213,"uid":88663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:09:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://share.881903.com/?news_id=1276734&amp;category_id=367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshare.881903.com%2F%3Fnew